      • guard

        public static void guard​(boolean predicate)
        All executions of Characteristic.specify(Object) which execute this method will be skipped and a new test case will be generated. Execution will be stopped if it is not possible to create a new test cases after a reasonable amount of tries.
        Parameters:
        predicate - Skip the current test case if the predicate is true.
